    <h1 class="h1 block__header">Contact Us</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="container block__inner">
    <div class="block__content">
      <p class="text-center">
        <strong>Please note that we do not run any frontline services. Please check for suitable organisations in the
          <a href="/find-help/">Find Help</a> section if you are experiencing homelessness and need support.</strong>
      </p>

      <div id="js-output" class="template"></div>

      <h2 class="h2">General enquiries</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, ideas, or would like to know more about us, you can get in touch at
        <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Locations</h2>
      <p>For questions specific to one of our locations, please contact our city admins at one of the following addresses:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:leeds@streetsupport.net">leeds@streetsupport.net</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:bradford@streetsupport.net">bradford@streetsupport.net</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:bournemouth@streetsupport.net">bournemouth@streetsupport.net</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:portsmouth@streetsupport.net">portsmouth@streetsupport.net</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:liverpool@streetsupport.net">liverpool@streetsupport.net</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="h2">Join the conversation</h2>
      <p>You can join the conversation on
        <a href="https://twitter.com/streetsupportuk">Twitter</a>,
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/streetsupport/">Facebook</a> or subscribe to
        <a href="http://streetsupport.us12.list-manage1.com/subscribe?u=da9a1d4bb2b1a69a981456972&id=52ba96f2af">our mailing list</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">In person</h2>
      <p>You are welcome to come and visit us in person at 111 Piccadilly, Manchester, M1 2HY. We are often out visiting
        organisations so please contact us first by emailing
        <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>, or you can contact Gary by phone on 07824 667709.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


